data.description: Owner Financing available up to $525,000 at 4.99% interest!!!!  Welcome to your paradise home in Northern Idaho!  Spanning over 20 subdividable acres of pristine land, this property provides the perfect canvas for your dreams of a serene & active lifestyle!  The home offers 5 bedrooms and 4 1/2 baths with an office, a basement family room, and a bar. There is a second in-law home offering 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths plus its own 1-car garage.  For those with a penchant for outdoor pursuits, the 24 x 40 shop offers ample storage for all of your recreational gear and as a bonus there is an 1800 sq ft workshop to play with all of your power tools.  Embrace the allure of Northern Idaho's landscapes, the elegance of luxurious living, and the endless possibilities this property offers.
